00:00:25.867 --> 00:00:27.721
in the forward direction.

00:00:27.721 --> 00:00:29.961
They're pretty cool and
you see them all the time

00:00:29.961 --> 00:00:31.887
in electronic components.

00:00:31.887 --> 00:00:34.235
So we're gonna figure
out how to use an LED

00:00:34.235 --> 00:00:36.902
