00:05:25.796 --> 00:05:27.629
one point on the line.

00:05:29.085 --> 00:05:30.255
But what else can I set to zero?

00:05:30.255 --> 00:05:31.931
I can set i equal to zero,

00:05:31.931 --> 00:05:34.931
which means I'm on the voltage axis.

00:05:35.935 --> 00:05:37.576
And what I'm actually gonna do

00:05:37.576 --> 00:05:39.674
is I'm just gonna look at my
circuit and figure this out

00:05:39.674 --> 00:05:41.174
